{"tid":1907894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【花式乃共】譚德塞：中国以外確診病例急增　韓意日伊朗疫情最應關注","createTime":"2020-03-03T02:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T02:00:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4573d853455839a11c54cd3c41756ad2298f07","tid":1907894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200303/s00005/2ac77405b624c1dccc2ff8b558a834ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200303%2Fs00005%2F2ac77405b624c1dccc2ff8b558a834ac.jpg&h=3e182793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞周一（2日）在瑞士日內瓦記者會上表示，中國過去24小時單日新增的新型冠狀病毒確診病例，為1月22日以來新低，但中國以外的國家，單日新增病例快速增加，比中國多近9倍。他稱，現時韓國、意大利、伊朗和日本的疫情最值得關注，病毒在全球傳播的風險非常高。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞認為，仍有機會控制疫情，又指出目前最令人關注的形勢不在中國。他稱，疫情爆發以來，中國以外有逾60個國家出現確診病例，迄今累計逾8700宗、127人死亡，主要來自韓國、意大利、伊朗和日本。另目前逾130多個國家尚未發現任何病例。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社/路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200303/s00005/1583196704636/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%AD%9A%E5%BE%B7%E5%A1%9E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E6%80%A5%E5%A2%9E-%E9%9F%93%E6%84%8F%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E6%9C%80%E6%87%89%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200303%2Fs00005%2F1583196704636%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%259A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%25A1%259E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E-%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2